textflow (0.2.9-4) jaunty; urgency=low

    New General Features
    -------------------------

      * New File Browser (LP:#241748)
      * Goto line bar (LP:#240185)
      * More snippets (LP:#254678, LP:#289870, LP:#301502)
      * Snippets definition syntax - Use '\' to escape next character (LP:#241384)
      * If TextFlow is already a open a new file will be opened in the same window (LP:#240268)
      * Convert whitespaces to tabs and tabs to whitespaces (LP:#242808, LP:#301689)
      * Move current line or selected lines up or down (LP:#242809)
      * Language Manager (LP:#243097, LP:#241383)
      * A help (LP:#240186)
      * Don't open 2 or more tabs for the same file (LP:#243304)
      * Remove search highlight when press ESC in search bar (LP:#274438)
      * When close the last tab open a new one blank (LP:#302873)
      * Add some shortcuts in menu (LP:#301114)
      
    Language Features
    -------------------------
      
      * Comment and uncomment lines for Python and Ruby
      * Run python script (LP:#252218)
      * Python and HTML auto indent (LP:#252219)
      * Auto close tags for HTML files (LP:#252220)
      * Ctrl+Return trigger to add "<br />" tag in HTML files (LP:#255878)
      * Ctrl+B trigger to add or surround the selection with "<strong></strong>" tags in HTML files
      * Ctrl+I trigger to add or surround the selection with "<emphasize></emphasize>" tags in HTML files

    Bugfixes
    -------------------------

      * Weird snippet completation (LP:#301117)
      * Undo all changes, don't remove "*" from name in tab (LP:#301735)
      * Some files with supported mime types doesn't appear in file browser (LP:#204269)  
      * Open/Save file dialog doesn't show extentionless files (LP:#280705)
      * Word complete weird behavior (LP:#291223)
      * Tab size returns to default value when file is saved (LP:#294955)
      * TextFlow snippet document must have XML header (LP:#305518)
      * TF Fail to start if atual directory in filebrowser is invalid/corrupt etc.. (LP:#313745)
      * Cannot open two files through file browser (LP:#290084)

 -- Yuri Malheiros <ymalheiros@gmail.com>  Mon, 06 Jul 2009 15:50:21 -0300
